### Hadith 3:759

*Narrated An-Nu'man bin Bashir:*

that his father took him to Allah's Apostle and said, "I have given this
son of mine a slave." The Prophet asked, "Have you given all your sons
the like?" He replied in the negative. The Prophet said, "Take back your
gift then."

